ency index is associated with a decline of 1% in the mobility\nindex. States with a high percentage of Democrat voters, large populations, and\nlocated in the west tend to be most compliant. A 10% rise in the proportion of\npeople voting Democrat is associated with a 5% increase in compliance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2022 10:09:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
