ting the Sedov-Taylor blast wave problem using strong and weak\nscaling tests. ScalSALE is executed and evaluated with both rezoning options -\nLagrangian and Eulerian.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2022 14:31:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
